+  4. one exact routing table from raw forced channels into the frozen
+     `mirror` / `companion` / `feedback` / `cross` partition so the overload
+     is admissibility-level rather than bookkeeping-level.
+- `[INFERRED]` Strongest claim this object is allowed to support now:
+  the repaired leakage sheet is the cleanest exact obstruction-facing object on
+  the frozen ledger, and the hostile `F_DT` comparator is already recorded as
+  an overload family in the same burden currency.
+- `[VERIFIED]` What the local record still does **not** justify:
+  a family-wide theorem for all `F_DT(delta, eta)`,
+  a claim that every repaired budget entry is hostile-sharp,
+  or an earned hostile counterexample before one explicit `F_DT` packet is
+  written on the frozen coefficient ledger.
+
+### 4. Why the two promoted objects should stay distinct at the handoff
+
+- `[INFERRED]` The repaired template object and the repaired leakage object
+  still ask different exact next questions on the same ledger:
+  the first is now a boundary-sharpness theorem test on one carried friendly
+  witness;
+  the second is an explicit hostile counterexample search in the live
+  obstruction currency.
