+### 5. Step-6 handoff memo
+
+- `[INFERRED]` If mission control keeps the survivor set live, the branch
+  handoff should be:
+  1. `Template-Defect Near-Closure` ->
+     first exact theorem test on the single carried witness `F_SL(1/16)`:
